node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Corey Funk on August 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: And we are off!!! Still can’t believe I sold my house and decided to travel the nation with @cobygrillo . So excited to share this next part of my journey with you guys! First stop, AZ, NM, and Texas! Where are you at?
